### StatusBar
  A horizontal layout component for displaying time and connectivity icons at the top of the screen.
  Import: `import { StatusBar } from 'test-client-design-system'`
  Props:
    - time: string (optional) — The current time to display.
    - className: string (optional) — Additional class names to apply to the component.

### NavigationBar
  NavigationBar component
  Import: `import { NavigationBar } from 'test-client-design-system'`
  Props:
    - title: string (required) — The title to display in the navigation bar.
    - size: 'sm' | 'md' | 'lg' (optional) — The size of the navigation bar.
'sm' for small, 'md' for medium, 'lg' for large.
    - variant: 'primary' | 'secondary' (optional) — The variant of the navigation bar.
'primary' for main navigation, 'secondary' for sub-navigation.
    - children: ReactNode (optional) — Additional icons or elements to display in the navigation bar.
    - className: string (optional) — Additional class names to apply to the navigation bar.

